1. *Ostaću* još malo na poslu da završim sve zadatke. (I will stay a bit longer at work to finish all tasks.)
2. Nadam se da *ostaću* zdrav ove zime. (I hope I will stay healthy this winter.)
3. *Ostaću* kod kuće ovog vikenda, umoran sam od putovanja. (I will stay at home this weekend, I'm tired from traveling.)
4. Ako *ostaću* duže, moraću da platim više za parking. (If I stay longer, I will have to pay more for parking.)
5. Ne znam koliko dugo *ostaću*, zavisi od toga koliko bude posla. (I don't know how long I will stay, it depends on how much work there is.)
6. *Ostaću* ovde sa tobom dok ne budeš spreman da odeš. (I will stay here with you until you're ready to go.)
7. Molim te, *ostaću* još samo pet minuta, ne mogu duže. (Please, let me stay for just five more minutes, I can't stay longer.)
8. Rekao sam mu da *ostaću* u gradu dok ne završim posao. (I told him that I will stay in the city until I finish my job.)
9. Ako *ostaću* ovde, moraću da se presvučem jer mi je hladno. (If I stay here, I will have to change because I'm cold.)
10. Nadam se da *ostaću* budan do kraja filma, jako mi se dopada. (I hope I will stay awake until the end of the movie, I really like it.)